Version-0.5.0 (Planning to release at Jun 29th, 2005)

  * Add bracket setting.
  * Add romaji customizing.
  * Add key-bindings theme.
    - First implementation has been done.
    - Should check duplicates of style file.
    - Other bug fixes/code improvement.
  * Fix for gcc-4.0

Version-0.6.0 (Planning to release at July 29th, 2005)

  * SKIM plugin.
  * Toggle upcase/downcase all or head of string on direct conversoin like
    Microsoft IME and ATOK.
  * Half width conversion like Microsoft IME and ATOK.
  * Add preedit color preference
  * Realtime conversion like honoka-tan.
  * Inline registering a word.
  * Add AZIK table.
  * Add T-Code.

Version-0.7.0 (Planning to release at Sep 29th, 2005)

  * Implement formal Kana typing method.
  * Search a character by Bushu (inline).
  * Search a character by code (inline).
  * Search a symbol (inline).
  * Provide more style files.
  * Add help.

Version-0.8.0 (Planning to release at Nov 29th, 2005)

Version-0.9.0 (Planning to release at Jan 29th, 2006)

Version-1.0.0 (Planning to release at Mar 29th, 2006)
